THE MEMENTO PATTERN
We use the Memento pattern to implement undo mechanism in our classes
In order to implement the single responsibility principle in our application, we cant store the current state and history in the same class.
COMPONENTS OF THE MEMENTO PATTERN
-The Originator class
 this is our main class, which should have a current state and an history.
-The Memento class
 this class represents the current state of our application.
-Caretaker class
 this class store the history of our application